prompt_text:
Write an executive summary for the {initiative_name} initiative, formatted as a {summary_type}. This summary will be reviewed by senior leadership, so it must be concise, data-informed, and action-oriented. Begin with a one-paragraph overview that captures the current state and strategic importance of the initiative.

Highlight the following key achievements:
{key_achievements}

Address any blockers or risks that require leadership attention:
{blockers_or_risks}

Conclude with clearly defined next steps and owners:
{next_steps}

The summary should follow a pyramid structure where the most critical information appears first, enabling executives to get the full picture from the opening paragraph alone. Use bullet points for scannability and quantify impact wherever possible.
